message.body: Today doesn't seem like it will be too bad. Fingers crossed. Can't wait to see you tonight. Have a good day.
That's a relief. I hope it's okay.
I can't wait to see you either
Yeah. Hah. I think my gas should be gone. But I'm feeling pretty weak and a little lightheaded.
You've inspired me to organize my workspace:
How did I inspire you? Haha. You're organized to begin with. Where'd you get those folders?
The supply closet
I want to decorate my desk
Well that's a start. I don't know what decorations are manly though.
I'm manly enough myself to not need it reflected in my decorations.
You threw out my bamboo but do you still have the jar with the rocks ?
I have the jar. Not the rocks. Mold was growing in it.
Okay
I'm going to Michelle's
Ok. I hope you don't get caught in the storms.
Me too. But I'm gonna go get some stuff for my desk
Really? We were just there for that!
I know. I didn't even thin k about looking into my Penn box

Ok. Well tomorrow would probably be better to do it since we're in for thunderstorms from 7 to 10 tonight. But it's up to you. Were also eating potato pancakes. Not that great. They'll be here if you want them later.
Yeah I'll eat them
I'm impatient
I have to go today
I know you are.
I'm waiting for the bus. Ive been for half an hour
Man. You could have walked home but it's so sticky.
You showered already?
Yeah and I don't want my lamp to get wet. I'm bringing it to work
Yeah
Oh great. We'll have no light in your room this weekend.
I have two other Lamps
Oh wait. I'm thinking cozy lighting. Those two aren't. But you have twinkle lights. Never mind.
This bus needs to hurry up!
I just got on
